3 Set up Query Parameters

duration_hours = 280
duration_text = paste(as.character(duration_hours), "h", sep = "")
print(duration_text)
## [1] "280h"
date_from = "2022-12-01 00:00:00"

#date_from = "2022-09-08 00:00:00"
BatteryID = "battery/1/logs"
query<-list(duration = duration_text, from = date_from, battery_ID = BatteryID , lendingtype="LNX",format="json")

jsonResponse<-GET(base_url ,query=query)

print(jsonResponse)
